A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: Star Wars: The Last Jedi feels forced\, unoriginal\, overproduced\, and unmemorable. This is Star Wars...not some Michael Bay film. This is a cheesy\, random Disney movie that wastes the time\, money\, intellect\, and imagination of an extremely dedicated and intelligent fan base on something wholly unmemorable. I was honestly waiting for Jar Jar Binks to grace us with a cameo. Star Wars fans are smarter than this\, expect more\, and deserve more. Do better.
